settings.c1:
Tempera strings won't be sold on any online store. We prefere to work together with professional instrument makers who are interested in sound as we are. We will soon release a list of partners here as soon. If you are interested in collaboration with us, please contact us. Lets speak about it.

An instrument is a system of many elements interacting with each other. The strings play an important role in this, but in spite of everything we are strongly dependent on a good setup and therefore on luthiers who know their craft.
settings.c2:
If want to try out the Tempera Strings, there is an easy way to do this:

Speak with your favorite bass maker / luthier about it.

We are interested to collaborate with instrument makers all over the world to ensure a perfect setup for the needs of our material on the instruments.
